00:02:11.039 --> 00:02:12.240
KEVIN NELSON: Yeah.

00:02:12.240 --> 00:02:13.950
My grandfather drank Schlitz.

00:02:13.950 --> 00:02:15.510
He was my introduction to beer.

00:02:15.510 --> 00:02:18.090
And when I was young,
