lot or something,

00:23:08.190 --> 00:23:11.340
and you wheeled it outside
into your parking lot

00:23:11.340 --> 00:23:13.290
in the cold enough
weather, there's

00:23:13.290 --> 00:23:14.829
natural yeast that
would inoculate.

00:23:14.829 --> 00:23:17.120
KEVIN NELSON: And we see some
brewers doing this today.

00:23:17.120 --> 00:23:20.420
They're doing some
wild yeast, definitely.

00:23:20.420 --> 00:23:23.490
JOHN HOLL: Yeah, that's like how
our nomadic ancestors did it.

