00:28:09.410 --> 00:28:12.980
today with these-- now we were
back up with more breweries,

00:28:12.980 --> 00:28:15.050
finally, from pre-Prohibition.

00:28:15.050 --> 00:28:16.250
JOHN HOLL: Yeah.

00:28:16.250 --> 00:28:19.410
It's easier to drink better
beer than ever before.

00:28:19.410 --> 00:28:20.700
And that's the thing.

