00:28:25.507 --> 00:28:26.090
And it's true.

00:28:26.090 --> 00:28:27.980
Just because you
can open a brewery

00:28:27.980 --> 00:28:30.710
doesn't mean that you're
going to make great beer.

00:28:30.710 --> 00:28:32.210
And so one of the
things, like I was

00:28:32.210 --> 00:28:34.040
talking about with--
if you see carbonation

00:28:34.040 --> 00:28:36.380
on the inside of
the glass, knowing

00:28:36.380 --> 00:28:38.870
some of the off flavors
that exist in beer.

00:28:38.870 --> 00:28:42.440
Like, if you taste
buttered popcorn,

00:28:42.440 --> 00:28:44.420
or you taste wet
cardboard or smell

00:28:44.420 --> 00:28:47.510
wet cardboard, or green apple.

00:28:47.510 --> 00:28:49.640
A lot of these things that
we know in general life

00:28:49.640 --> 00:28:53.600
are considered to be flaws
when it comes to beer.

00:28:53.600 --> 00:28:56.300
You don't want to taste
buttered popcorn in your stout.

00:28:56.300 --> 00:28:58.340
You don't want to
taste it in your lager.

00:28:58.340 --> 00:29:03.680
You don't want to taste skunk
in your Dutch lager as well.

00:29:03.680 --> 00:29:06.020
But we all know
that with Heineken,

00:29:06.020 --> 00:29:08.330
and we kind of give
that a pass, right?

00:29:08.330 --> 00:29:10.670
So, like, my dad
was drinking it.

00:29:10.670 --> 00:29:13.160
But that happens because
the light comes in,

00:29:13.160 --> 00:29:15.980
and the blue UV ray
negatively interacts

00:29:15.980 --> 00:29:19.130
with the alpha acids
inside of hops and turns

00:29:19.130 --> 00:29:22.030
hops to taste like skunk.

00:29:22.030 --> 00:29:24.010
And it's something
that we all know.

00:29:24.010 --> 00:29:27.950
But skunk in marijuana
sometimes is kind of desirable.

00:29:27.950 --> 00:29:30.550
So it's these picking
and choosing things.

00:29:30.550 --> 00:29:32.860
But when brewers are
putting stuff out,

00:29:32.860 --> 00:29:37.040
and you taste these
things at a local brewery,

00:29:37.040 --> 00:29:39.620
it doesn't necessarily mean
that they're making great beer.

00:29:39.620 --> 00:29:41.120
And that's a larger
problem as well.

00:29:41.120 --> 00:29:43.340
So with so much choice
come so much great,

00:29:43.340 --> 00:29:45.211
because also you
